                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Springer</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Rockhill</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-12-23"><hi rend="italic">December 23,
                                    1896</hi></date>.<lb/>(Received December 30,
                            1896.)</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Trial of Sanguily commenced Monday. Finished to-day. Sentence within
